with open(''index.html'', ''r'', encoding=''utf-8'') as f:

# Define sections
market_start = 1381  # Line 1382 (0-indexed)

# Write the updated content
with open(''index.html'', ''w'', encoding=''utf-8'') as f:
    f.writelines(final_lines)
